title: 859. Teams Under Pressure in Week 2 & Breakout Candidates
itunes:title: 859. Teams Under Pressure in Week 2 & Breakout Candidates
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss which teams are under the most pressure heading into Week 2. Then, the pair each give an under-the-radar breakout candidate. To wrap up the show, the duo preview the Marshall vs Bowling Green game on NFL Network and highlight a player to watch out for.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
